ў system requirements:

  Sorry guys, but this intro was designed for my computer, so it runs ok on
  486DX33. I know it's a new kind of disease - but i think routines are
  optimised a lot and all kinds of interference stuff are very time consuming.

ў creating story:

  Well, about 3 months ago i decided to make some cute demo and started to work
  on some nice effects. I wanted to modify existing plasma effect.
  So i developed a double plasma (that in small window) and a fade plasma (full
  screen hellfire :)). I find these effects original and very nice and decided
  to implement them into my 4Kintro. So now you know for sure why it is called
  Plasmatic. I wanted also add RGB plasma in fake mode - but maybe later.
  Then, who was not amazed by bootmagic and great satori proggies in it?
  Me too and i was wondering about animating this great thing. You see the
  result. Not in some great scale, but i think it doesn't mind. The rest of
  implemented effect are not so great, but they were created my minimal
  modification of satori routine, so i whould be fool not to include them.
  And i think that's the only way how to creat a decet 4Kintro. Hope you find
  Plasmatic as a decet one... Good luck,

   Zden

